WeZfoJiWl4p-EtoF-dwee&amp;ust=1545963982005820</a>"},{"pid":"4d01d11945a9f872c66224cfbde8ad378c384aa3","tid":957283,"uid":106026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"呢啲預言每次都講到下一年係世界末日咁,講足咁多年總有一次中,然後啲人就當個所謂先知神咁拜.<br />\n之前又係呢啲先知出黎話北京奧運係最後一屆奧運,到而家都就黎東京奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3208d5125299874a56fac73a1da08b47826f6ea5","tid":957283,"uid":106026,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fc4b39afca57a7b70206814a637576aff1a40e3b","tid":957283,"uid":1251,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"2017年尾既新聞有佢對2018年既預測<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇個中<br />\n中國會取代美國做世界大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有係金星發現新品種既能源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/url?sa=i&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwicupDh-r7fAhUKa94KHRilA7wQzPwBegQIARAC&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Flifestyle%2Fviral-and-trending%2F251217%2Fblind-mystic-baba-vanga-has-two-major-predictions-for-2018.html&amp;psig=AOvVaw3WeZfoJiWl4p-EtoF-dwee&amp;ust=1545963982005820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.jp%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26ved%3D2ahUKEwicupDh-r7fAhUKa94KHRilA7wQzPwBegQIARAC%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%252Flifestyle%252Fviral-and-trending%252F251217%252Fblind-mystic-baba-vanga-has-two-major-predictions-for-2018.html%26psig%3DAOvVaw3WeZfoJiWl4p-EtoF-dwee%26ust%3D1545963982005820&d=i5rxKKHPmPy3CA6H%2Fw9zAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=09f7bf0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.jp/url?sa=i&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwicupDh-r7fAhUKa94KHRilA7wQzPwBegQIARAC&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Flifestyle%2Fviral-and-trending%2F251217%2Fblind-mystic-baba-vanga-has-two-major-predictions-for-2018.html&a